t talked about, and probably no time, which is setting up a new Centre of Art and Technology, which is the mayor\rquote s great obsession down there. That\rquote s very exciting, by the way.  And I did do that very big study with Manuel, }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \i\f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6447803\charrsid6447803 Technopoles of the World}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid6447803\charrsid6447803 
