 with this new Centre of Art and Technology, with a new mayor \endash  so that\rquote s all right!  And the mayor just got back in by the skin of his teeth, he was the only Socialist mayor to get back in in the recent elections in Spain, so we\rquote 
re still working with him there, yes.
