s called SINTROPHER \endash  which stands for Sustainable Integrated Tram-based Transport Options for Peripheral European Regions \endash  and I invented that, and have regretted it ever since.  But anyway, we\rquote 
re stuck with it.  What we tried to do is get a technology they invented in Germany, in Karlsruhe and then used in Kass}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\lang2057\langfe2057\langnp2057\insrsid16151394 el, which is a partner, called \lquote 
